{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"3a41af49-90f3-40ed-b0da-750ca650890a","content":"Here's what you need:\n\n### Environment Variables\n\nFor NativeAOT, the runtime **doesn't bundle** createdump, so you must point it explicitly:\n\n| Variable | Value | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump` | `1` | Enable automatic dumps on crash |\n| `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType` | `4` | Full dump (1=Mini, 2=Heap, 3=Triage, 4=Full) |\n| `DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName` | `/tmp/dumps/core.%p.%t` | Dump path pattern (`%p`=PID, `%t`=timestamp) |\n| `DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath` | `/opt/tools/createdump` | **Required for NativeAOT** — tells the runtime where createdump lives |\n\n### Pod Spec Changes\n\n```yaml\nspec:\n  containers:\n    - name: your-app\n      # ... image, ports, etc.\n      env:\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgEnableMiniDump\n          value: \"1\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpType\n          value: \"4\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgMiniDumpName\n          value: \"/tmp/dumps/core.%p.%t\"\n        - name: DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath\n          value: \"/opt/tools/createdump\"\n      securityContext:\n        capabilities:\n          add:\n            - SYS_PTRACE          # createdump uses ptrace to attach\n      volumeMounts:\n        - name: crash-dumps\n          mountPath: /tmp/dumps\n  volumes:\n    - name: crash-dumps\n      emptyDir:\n        sizeLimit: 2Gi           # adjust based on your app's memory footprint\n```\n\n### Key points\n\n- **`SYS_PTRACE`** is mandatory — `createdump` uses `ptrace()` to read the crashing process's memory.\n- **`DOTNET_DbgCreatedumpPath`** is the critical one for NativeAOT; without it the runtime has no way to find `createdump` (CoreCLR bundles it, NativeAOT does not).\n- Use `emptyDir` for ephemeral collection; swap to a **PersistentVolumeClaim** if you need dumps to survive pod restarts.\n- Set `DbgMiniDumpType` to `2` (Heap) instead of `4` (Full) to reduce dump size if you don't need thread register context.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"bda9fe5e-f157-4033-b883-dee848bebbc6","outputTokens":639,"requestId":"F881:203D52:528E285:5AE2AC6:69F9FFF1"},"id":"415ca682-1508-4704-9445-bf7f98d5c56c","timestamp":"2026-05-05T14:34:42.257Z","parentId":"d424fe58-c931-4bf6-9fb2-b2f89c63cdf4"}
